Detect BOM

find . -type f -print0 | xargs -0r awk '/^\xEF\xBB\xBF/ {print FILENAME} {nextfile}' > bom

http://muzso.hu/2011/11/08/using-awk-sed-to-detect-remove-the-byte-order-mark-bom

C-x RET f

Change from utf-8-with-signature to ut8-8

